this is the second meet-up for the new product of television remote control , with a particular focus on its functional design .
industrial designer , marketing and user interface were each invited to give a presentation on the subject that they are in charge of .
on the basis of conducted user requirement survey , industrial designer and user interface put forward their ideas on remote control features which are new to the existing market , along with the functionality and outlook of the product .
among all the features , speech recognition command takes up the majority of discussed subjects .
the group also discussed the material appropriate to use in the construction .
after the group determined the financial target of this project , as well as the production price and reasonable selling price , marketing suggested taking a risk in price rise .
